@startuml
title Event Trace Diagrams - Library Patron Interactions

skinparam maxMessageSize 60
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

autonumber

actor Patron
participant "Library System" as LS
database DB

== Scenario 1: Search for a Book ==

Patron -> LS: Enter search query
LS -> DB: Search for books
DB --> LS: Return results
LS --> Patron: Display results


== Scenario 2: Borrow a Book ==

Patron -> LS: Request to borrow book
LS -> DB: Check availability
DB --> LS: Available

LS -> DB: Create loan record
LS -> DB: Mark book as borrowed
DB --> LS: Update confirmed

LS --> Patron: Borrow confirmed


== Scenario 3: Return a Book ==

Patron -> LS: Return book
LS -> DB: Update loan status
DB --> LS: Return recorded

LS --> Patron: Return confirmation

@enduml
